com.opengamma.strata.market.id

Class DiscountCurveId

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.market.id.DiscountCurveId
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MarketDataId<Curve>, CurveId, RateCurveId, Serializable, Bean, ImmutableBean

    public final class DiscountCurveId
extends Object
implements RateCurveId, ImmutableBean, Serializable
    Market data ID identifying the discount curve for a currency.

    This is used when there is a need to obtain an instance of Curve that can be used to determine discount factors.
